                <seg>
                    <tei:milestone xml:id="UT22084-068-007-29"/>“Maitreya, sons or daughters of the lineage with sincere faith should recite the names of these twelve tathāgata, arhat, perfect and complete buddhas, and over the course of ten days as they confess all their misdeeds,</seg>
