            </tuv>
	<tuv xml:lang="en">
                <seg>As they take rebirth in cyclic existence, they will have the support of the excellent conditions of good looks and wealth, the excellent conditions of family line, the excellent conditions of social standing, the excellent conditions of family traits,<tei:note xml:id="UT22084-068-007-32"/> the excellent conditions of appearance, and the excellent conditions of having a retinue of people around them who are of similar disposition.</seg>
            </tuv>
